cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper involves image processing and machine learning techniques for facial expression recognition, which are commonly associated with computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of deep autoencoders also suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper may also fall under multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category as it deals with processing and analyzing facial images.
